config.cgm.server.projectile_spread.max_count=Max Count
config.cgm.server.projectile_spread.max_count.tooltip=The amount of times a player has too shoot within the spread threshold before the maximum amount of spread is applied. Setting the value higher means it will take longer for the spread to be applied.

